# Color Usage Guidelines

## Custom Colors
- Always use custom colors defined in colors.tsx instead of basic color values
- Avoid using raw color values (like '#f8fafc' or 'white') directly in components
- Import and reference color tokens from the colors.tsx file
- This ensures consistent theming and easier maintenance across the application
